Alstom Looks at French Ports for Wind-Power Site, Les Echos Says

-- B y   H e a t h e r   S m i t h
-- 
2011-06-06T05:34:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/alstom-looks-at-french-ports-for-wind-power-site-les-echos-says.html
Alstom SA (ALO)  is talking to French ports
along the Atlantic Ocean and the English Channel to find a site
for a wind-power park that would supply energy to the local area
and elsewhere, including Germany and Belgium, by 2014,  Les Echos 
reported today, citing an Alstom official.  The company is also looking at sites in England to serve
the British market, the newspaper said, citing Frederic
Hendrick, the vice president for offshore activities at Alstom
Power.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Heather Smith in Paris at 
 hsmith26@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anthony Aarons at   aaarons@bloomberg.net . 